    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fcdfcf4b5cdb414a4fef268c5dc54843.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fcdfcf4b5cdb414a4fef268c5dc54843.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fcdfcf4b5cdb414a4fef268c5dc54843.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblin Scout: I Won't Let You Level Up In My Monster Village, Our Strongest Warrior Will Use My Equipment To Beat You Up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a goblin scout living in a goblin town. You might not be the strongest goblin in town, but you are the fastest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your town comes under attack by heroes that are trying to level up, the town's strongest fighter goes out to meet them in turn based Active Time Battle. On his own he is too weak to defeat even the weakest of heroes. You, as the fastest in town, must bring him the items and equipment he needs to fight off these XP grinding heroes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game includes: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fa8b69509ede2f5e8177f6a118daffd3.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fa8b69509ede2f5e8177f6a118daffd3.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/fa8b69509ede2f5e8177f6a118daffd3.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Active Time Turn based combat <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/1930f804baaaa6e49045516415ab4148.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/1930f804baaaa6e49045516415ab4148.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/1930f804baaaa6e49045516415ab4148.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- First person platforming<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/9af563457391777ef9042a4d2e19740a.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/9af563457391777ef9042a4d2e19740a.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/9af563457391777ef9042a4d2e19740a.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The above two at the same time in fact<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/13c3e0470feb8b936ea1b2c9ec47a08b.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/13c3e0470feb8b936ea1b2c9ec47a08b.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/13c3e0470feb8b936ea1b2c9ec47a08b.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Short term resource and time management<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/d0d27c726a6c478edebd0a58a0ce1c0a.poster.avif?t=1771839923\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/d0d27c726a6c478edebd0a58a0ce1c0a.webm?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019490/extras/d0d27c726a6c478edebd0a58a0ce1c0a.mp4?t=1771839923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Silly dialogue with your neighbours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A short playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an expanded version of a game made for Miziziziz' 4 Devs 1 Artkit series of videos.</p>",
